WEBVTT

00:15:27.746 --> 00:15:30.385
How could they know the rain would end?

00:15:30.385 --> 00:15:34.327
This bugged me and I was befuddled.

00:15:34.327 --> 00:15:35.773
How could he know that?

00:15:35.773 --> 00:15:39.536
Some months later,
I met him at another event and said,

00:15:39.536 --> 00:15:45.342
"Davi, how did you know that if the forest
was destroyed, there'd be no more rain?"

00:15:45.342 --> 00:15:50.157
He replied:
"The spirit of the forest told us."

00:15:50.157 --> 00:15:54.744
For me, this was a game changer,

00:15:54.744 --> 00:15:56.447
a radical change.

00:15:56.447 --> 00:15:57.866
I said, "Gosh!

00:15:57.866 --> 00:16:02.105
Why am I doing all this science